AC:

* The EBIS/DPL API will be updated to consume the Top 300 flag from DPL
* This will flag will be visible on:
** Social Media Monitoring widget
** Player Profiles
** Top 300 widget
* Will need to update the data in ebis for the past several years to get back in sync with DPL

Endpoint is:

ebis2-core-services/dpl/top300/{year}

Post BODY for the end point is a list of player Ids:


{code:json}{
    "playerIds":[
        760965,5026545
    ]
}{code}
